<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Bluebu</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'style' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.3.2/jquery.min.js","root", :catch=>true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tag %>
</head>
<body>

<%#= yield %>
<!-- Contains and centers the page -->
<div id="background-glow">
<div id="container-wrap">
<div id="container">
    <!-- Header - logo and navigation -->
    <div id="header">
        <!-- 'Floating' logo -->

        <h1><span>Hi-Ruby中文站即将启航</span></h1>
        <!-- Navigation -->
        <ol id="navigation">
            <!-- Use this id to identify the active page -->
            <li id="active-page"><a href="/">首页</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">博客</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">代码库</a></li>

            <li><a href="#">其他</a></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Intro lead text -->
    <div class="intro">
        <img src="/images/root/intro.png" alt="Hi, my name is Mike and I'm a freelance web designer. I take your ideas and turn them into gold without breaking the bank. Please browse through my work and contact me if you have any questions." />
    </div>

    <!-- Latest project -->
    <h2 id="latest-project-title"><img src="/images/root/titles/latest-project.png" alt="Latest project" /></h2>
    <div id="latest-project">
        <div class="preview">
            <a href="#" class="changer prev"><img src="/images/root/change-prev.png" alt="Previous item" /></a>
            <a href="#" class="changer next"><img src="/images/root/change-next.png" alt="Next item" /></a>
            <img src="/images/root/projects/panda.png" alt="Panda Sofas" class="image" />
        </div>
        <div class="descr">

            <h3 class="title">Panda Sofas</h3>
            <p class="description">Panda Sofas approached me with a vision. They wanted a warm interior themed website with basic functions and they wanted it in time for their grand opening a week later. Total project completion time was 48 hours of grinding but it was well worth it.</p>
            <p class="actions"><a href="#">Launch</a> <a href="#">Details</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Past work -->

    <h2><img src="/images/root/titles/past-work.png" alt="Past work" /></h2>
    <div id="past-work">
        <p class="item"><a href="#"><img src="/images/root/work/reinvigorate.png" alt="Reinvigorate" /></a></p>
        <p class="item"><a href="#"><img src="/images/root/work/pulse.png" alt="Pulse" /></a></p>
        <p class="item"><a href="#"><img src="/images/root/work/mobify.png" alt="Mobify" /></a></p>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->

    <div id="footer">
        <div class="contact">
            <h2><img src="/images/root/titles/contact.png" alt="Contact Me" /></h2>
            <p class="lead">Whew! You made it! If you have any questions or simply want to hire me, continue reading:</p>
            <p><strong>PH</strong>: 978 844 5535</p>
            <p><strong>EM</strong>: designer@myportfolio.com</p>

        </div>
        <div class="about">
            <h2><img src="/images/root/titles/about.png" alt="About Me" /></h2>
            <p>I've been in the design game for about 5 years now. I honestly can't remember what got me started with web design but I know I don't regret getting into it. It's such a dynamic industry so I'm always on my toes. I'm a college student and I'm trying to make a living however I can.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
